{
  "id": "69b1b5412367ae1ef575daf4",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:パターナリズム",
  "created": 1773253982,
  "updated": 1773306008,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b1b5412367ae1ef575daf4",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:パターナリズム",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253982,
      "updated": 1773253982
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55d00000000003eb176",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（進行）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253982,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb177",
      "text": "ねえねえ、今日のテーマは「[パターナリズム]」なんだけどさ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb178",
      "text": "ぶっちゃけこれ、むずワードすぎん？ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb179",
      "text": "ざっくり言うと、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb17a",
      "text": "「本人のためだよ〜」って言って、他の人が決めちゃうやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb17b",
      "text": "たとえばさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb17c",
      "text": "「危ないからこのゲームはダメ！」とか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb17d",
      "text": "「健康のためにこの食べ物は禁止！」みたいな。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb17e",
      "text": "親とか先生がやりがちだけど、社会でもあるらしい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb17f",
      "text": "今日はこのへんをゆる〜く語ろうぜって感じ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb180",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb181",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb182",
      "text": "ええ、とても興味深い言葉ですわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb183",
      "text": "「あなたのためを思って」と言われると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb184",
      "text": "人はつい従ってしまうものですもの。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb185",
      "text": "けれども、その言葉には",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb186",
      "text": "まるで親が子を守ろうとするような…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb187",
      "text": "優しさと、少しの支配が混ざっているように感じます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb188",
      "text": "まるで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb189",
      "text": "大きな木が若い芽を覆い守るようでありながら、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb18a",
      "text": "同時に日光を遮ってしまうような…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb18b",
      "text": "そういう微妙な関係なのではないかしら。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb18c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb18d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb18e",
      "text": "概念としては、その理解で概ね正確。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb18f",
      "text": "パターナリズムは政治哲学や倫理学の用語で、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb190",
      "text": "[** 「本人の利益のために、本人の自由を制限する行為」]と定義されることが多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb191",
      "text": "例えば次のような政策。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb192",
      "text": " シートベルト着用義務",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb193",
      "text": " 薬物規制",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb194",
      "text": " 未成年の飲酒禁止",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb195",
      "text": "典型例は[ジョン・スチュアート・ミル]の議論。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773283700
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb196",
      "text": "彼は基本的に反対の立場だった。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb197",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb198",
      "text": "John Stuart Mill On Liberty",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb199",
      "text": "https://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/34901",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb19a",
      "text": "要点をまとめる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb19b",
      "text": " 1. 自分に害があるだけなら国家は介入すべきでない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb19c",
      "text": " 2. 他人に害が及ぶ場合のみ介入は正当化される",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb19d",
      "text": "これを[** [危害原則]（harm principle）]という。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773305813
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb19e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb19f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1a0",
      "text": "おおー、「危害原則」ってやつか！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1a1",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1a2",
      "text": "「自爆するだけなら自己責任」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1a3",
      "text": "「他人巻き込むならストップ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1a4",
      "text": "みたいな感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1a5",
      "text": "なんかゲームでいうと、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1a6",
      "text": "ソロプレイなら好きにやれ、マルチなら迷惑かけんな",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1a7",
      "text": "ってルールっぽいｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1a9",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1aa",
      "text": "かなり近い例え。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ab",
      "text": "ただし現実社会では議論が複雑。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ac",
      "text": "例えばヘルメット義務。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ad",
      "text": "　転んでケガする → 本人の問題",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ae",
      "text": "　しかし医療費は社会が負担する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1af",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1b0",
      "text": "個人の選択が社会コストになる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1b1",
      "text": "このため、完全な自由主義は成立しにくい。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1b3",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1b4",
      "text": "なるほど…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1b5",
      "text": "一人の選択が、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1b6",
      "text": "まるで湖に落ちた小石のように",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1b7",
      "text": "波紋を広げてしまうのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1b8",
      "text": "そう考えると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1b9",
      "text": "「自分だけの問題」と言い切るのは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ba",
      "text": "少し難しい気もいたします。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1bb",
      "text": "けれども、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1bc",
      "text": "あまりに人を守ろうとしすぎると…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1bd",
      "text": "人は自分で歩くことを",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1be",
      "text": "忘れてしまうかもしれませんわね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1bf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1c0",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1c1",
      "text": "あー、それわかる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1c2",
      "text": "なんかさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1c3",
      "text": "全部「危ないから禁止！」ってされたら",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1c4",
      "text": "人生チュートリアルのまま終わる感あるよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1c5",
      "text": "レベル1から進まないやつｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1c7",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1c8",
      "text": "良い比喩。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1c9",
      "text": "実際、その問題を解決するために",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ca",
      "text": "最近は別の考え方が提案されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1cb",
      "text": "[リバタリアン・パターナリズム]（libertarian paternalism）。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773305999
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1cc",
      "text": "要するに",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1cd",
      "text": "　強制はしない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ce",
      "text": "　しかし良い選択をしやすくする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1cf",
      "text": "という方法。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1d0",
      "text": "代表例：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1d1",
      "text": "　健康的な食品を目立つ場所に置く",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1d2",
      "text": "　年金加入を「自動登録」にする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1d3",
      "text": "人は選べるが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1d4",
      "text": "自然と良い方向に誘導される。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1d5",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1d6",
      "text": "https://www.nudge.org/",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1d7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1d8",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1d9",
      "text": "あ！それ聞いたことある！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1da",
      "text": "[** [ナッジ]（nudge）]ってやつでしょ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773306008
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1db",
      "text": "「肘でちょいってつつく」みたいな意味の。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1dc",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1dd",
      "text": "禁止 → ✕",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1de",
      "text": "こっちのほうが楽だよ → ◎",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1df",
      "text": "って誘導するやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1e0",
      "text": "ゲームUIみたいだなｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1e1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1e2",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1e3",
      "text": "とても優しい方法のように思えますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1e4",
      "text": "人を縛るのではなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1e5",
      "text": "そっと背中を押す。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1e6",
      "text": "それはまるで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1e7",
      "text": "本のしおりのようです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1e8",
      "text": "どこへ進むかは読者が決めるけれど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1e9",
      "text": "次のページを開きやすくしてくれる…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ea",
      "text": "そんな気遣いの形なのかもしれません。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1eb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ec",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ed",
      "text": "ただし批判もある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ee",
      "text": "ナッジは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ef",
      "text": "「見えない操作ではないか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1f0",
      "text": "という問題。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1f1",
      "text": "本人が気づかないうちに",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1f2",
      "text": "選択が設計されている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1f3",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1f4",
      "text": "自由に見えて",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1f5",
      "text": "設計者の意図がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1f7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1f8",
      "text": "うわ、それちょっと怖いやつじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1f9",
      "text": "「自由に選んでね！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1fa",
      "text": "↓",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1fb",
      "text": "実は選ばされてました",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1fc",
      "text": "みたいなｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1fd",
      "text": "ゲームで言うと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1fe",
      "text": "選択肢A",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb1ff",
      "text": "選択肢A（おすすめ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb200",
      "text": "みたいなやつ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb201",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb202",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb203",
      "text": "けれど…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb204",
      "text": "人は完全に自由でいることも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb205",
      "text": "ときに難しいものです。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb206",
      "text": "迷いの森に入ったとき、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb207",
      "text": "小さな道しるべがあるだけで",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb208",
      "text": "安心することもありますから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb209",
      "text": "大切なのは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb20a",
      "text": "その道しるべが",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb20b",
      "text": "人をどこへ導こうとしているのか…。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb20c",
      "text": "それを誠実に示すことなのかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb20d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb20e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb20f",
      "text": "同意。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb210",
      "text": "ここまでの要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb211",
      "text": "パターナリズムの論点",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb212",
      "text": " 1. 本人のために自由を制限してよいのか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb213",
      "text": " 2. 個人の選択は社会に影響する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb214",
      "text": " 3. 強制ではなく誘導（ナッジ）という方法",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb215",
      "text": " 4. しかし誘導も操作になり得る",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb216",
      "text": "結局、問題は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb217",
      "text": "誰が、どこまで決めてよいのか。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb218",
      "text": "これは政治哲学の中心テーマ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb219",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb21a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（まとめ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb21b",
      "text": "いや〜今日の話、けっこう深かったな！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb21c",
      "text": "まとめると",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb21d",
      "text": " 「君のためだよ！」って自由を制限するのがパターナリズム",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb21e",
      "text": " でも社会だと完全自由もムズい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb21f",
      "text": " だから「ナッジ」みたいなやり方が出てきた",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb220",
      "text": " でもそれも操作っぽい問題ある",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb221",
      "text": "って感じだね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb222",
      "text": "つまり結論は…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb223",
      "text": "人を守るのと、自由を尊重するののバランスむずすぎ問題ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773253983,
      "updated": 1773253983
    },
    {
      "id": "69b1b55e00000000003eb224",
      "text": "ってことか。",
